                </annotation>
                <annotation id="3">
                    <infon key="type">webanno.custom.Phenotypes</infon>
                    <infon key="HPOterm">http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/HP_0001623</infon>
                    <location length="19" offset="16"/>
                    <text>breech presentation</text>
                </annotation>
            </sentence>
            <sentence>
                <offset>325</offset>
                <text>At birth, the proband weighed 3.6 kg (67th centile), measured 48.3 cm (34th centile) in length, and 35 cm (57th centile) as the head circumference.</text>
            </sentence>
            <sentence>
                <offset>473</offset>
                <text>The proband was noted to have flat facies, mildly prominent eyes, flat nasal bridge, upturned nasal tip, posteriorly rotated ears, micrognathia, glossoptosis, complete cleft palate, short neck, short limbs, brachydactyly (two–five fingers), and sandal gap.</text>
