            <sentence>
                <offset>730</offset>
                <text>There was no limitation of joint movements, and evidence of pectus and spine abnormalities on examination.</text>
            </sentence>
            <sentence>
                <offset>837</offset>
                <text>The assessment of X-rays at birth showed poorly calcified vertebrae and vertebral bodies, short dumbbell femurs with metaphyseal flaring, short metacarpals, and phalanges.</text>
