                </annotation>
            </sentence>
            <sentence>
                <offset>1140</offset>
                <text>At 2 months of age, although the proband had short limbs with a bowed tibia and fibula, we observed that the features of skeletal dysplasia and dysmorphic features were less obvious compared with birth.</text>
