                    <location length="12" offset="146"/>
                    <text>micrognathia</text>
                </annotation>
            </sentence>
            <sentence>
                <offset>1646</offset>
                <text>The proband's developmental milestones were age appropriate, and no similar disease history was noted in her siblings or other family members.</text>
            </sentence>
            <sentence>
                <offset>1792</offset>
                <text>Whole exome sequencing using available commercial methods in the proband revealed two heterozygous variants, c.190 C &gt; T and c.339_340delCCinsG in exons 2 and 3 of COL11A2 , respectively.</text>
            </sentence>
